const Footer = () => {\r
  const container = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\r
  const [Send, cilentData] = useNewsLetter()\r
  const [openPopup, setOpenPopUp] = useState(false)\r
  const ref = useRef(null)\r
  const isInView = useInView(ref)\r
\r
  const variants = {\r
    visible: (i: any) => ({\r
      translateY: 0,\r
      transition: {\r
        type: 'spring',\r
        stiffness: 100,\r
        damping: 12,\r
        duration: 0.4,\r
        delay: i * 0.03,\r
      },\r
    }),\r
\r
    hidden: { translateY: 200 },\r
  }\r
  const handleNewsLetterData = (e: FormEvent) => {\r
    e.preventDefault()\r
    console.log(e)\r
    e.preventDefault()\r
    const target = e.target as HTMLFormElement\r
    const formData = new FormData(target)\r
\r
    const clientEmail = formData.get('newsletter_email')!\r
\r
    const data: ClientData = {\r
      email: clientEmail.toString(),\r
    }\r
\r
    Send(data)\r
    setOpenPopUp(true)\r
    target.reset()\r
    if (setOpenPopUp) {\r
      setTimeout(() => {\r
        setOpenPopUp(false)\r
      }, 2000)\r
    }\r
  }\r
\r
  return (\r
    <>\r
      <Toast.Provider>\r
        <Toast.Provider swipeDirection="right">\r
          <Toast.Root\r
            className="ToastRoot"\r
            open={openPopup}\r
            onOpenChange={setOpenPopUp}\r
          >\r
            <Toast.Title className="ToastTitle">\r
              We Received Your Message, Thanks\r
            </Toast.Title>\r
            <Toast.Action\r
              className="ToastAction"\r
              asChild\r
              altText="Goto schedule to undo"\r
            >\r
              <button className="bg-white text-black px-3 py-1 rounded-lg">\r
                ok\r
              </button>\r
            </Toast.Action>\r
          </Toast.Root>\r
          <Toast.Viewport className="ToastViewport" />\r
        </Toast.Provider>\r
        <Toast.Viewport />\r
      </Toast.Provider>\r
\r
      <div\r
        className="relative h-full sm:pt-14 pt-8 bg-[#f7f7f7] text-black"\r
        ref={container}\r
      >\r
        <div className="sm:container  px-4 mx-auto">\r
          <div className="md:flex justify-between w-full">\r
            <div>\r
              <h1 className="md:text-4xl text-2xl font-semibold">\r
                Let‘s do great work together\r
              </h1>\r
              <div className="pt-2 pb-6 md:w-99  ">\r
                <p className="md:text-2xl text-xl  py-4">\r
                  Sign up for our newsletter*\r
                </p>\r
                <div className=" hover-button relative bg-black flex justify-between items-center border-2 overflow-hidden  border-black rounded-full  text-white hover:text-black md:text-2xl">\r
                  <form\r
                    onSubmit={(e) => handleNewsLetterData(e)}\r
                    className="relative z-2 grid grid-cols-6  w-full h-full"\r
                  >\r
                    <input\r
                      type="email"\r
                      name="newsletter_email"\r
                      className="border-none bg-transparent  py-3 px-6  col-span-5"\r
                      placeholder="Your Email * "\r
                    />{' '}\r
                    <button\r
                      type="submit"\r
                      className="cursor-pointer w-full hover:bg-primaryColor bg-white text-white h-full cols-span-1"\r
                    >\r
                      <svg\r
                        width="15"\r
                        height="15"\r
                        viewBox="0 0 15 15"\r
                        fill="none"\r
                        className="w-full h-[80%] "\r
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"\r
                      >\r
                        <path\r
                          d="M8.14645 3.14645C8.34171 2.95118 8.65829 2.95118 8.85355 3.14645L12.8536 7.14645C13.0488 7.34171 13.0488 7.65829 12.8536 7.85355L8.85355 11.8536C8.65829 12.0488 8.34171 12.0488 8.14645 11.8536C7.95118 11.6583 7.95118 11.3417 8.14645 11.1464L11.2929 8H2.5C2.22386 8 2 7.77614 2 7.5C2 7.22386 2.22386 7 2.5 7H11.2929L8.14645 3.85355C7.95118 3.65829 7.95118 3.34171 8.14645 3.14645Z"\r
                          fill="#000"\r
                          fillRule="evenodd"\r
                          clipRule="evenodd"\r
                        ></path>\r
                      </svg>\r
                    </button>\r
                  </form>\r
                </div>\r
              </div>\r
            </div>\r
            <div className="flex gap-10">\r
              <ul>\r
                <li className="text-2xl pb-2 text-black font-semibold">\r
                  SITEMAP\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/">Home</Link>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/about">About us</Link>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/services">Our Services</Link>\r
                </li>\r
\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/projects">Projects</Link>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/blogs">Blogs</Link>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <Link href="/contact-us">Contact</Link>\r
                </li>\r
              </ul>\r
              <ul>\r
                <li className="text-2xl pb-2 text-black font-semibold">\r
                  SOCIAL\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <a\r
                    href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/next-codez/"\r
                    target="_blank"\r
                    className="underline"\r
                  >\r
                    LinkedIn\r
                  </a>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <a\r
                    href="https://twitter.com/NextCodez"\r
                    target="_blank"\r
                    className="underline"\r
                  >\r
                    Twitter\r
                  </a>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <a\r
                    href="https://www.instagram.com/nextcodez/"\r
                    target="_blank"\r
                    className="underline"\r
                  >\r
                    Instagram\r
                  </a>\r
                </li>\r
                <li className="text-xl font-medium">\r
                  <a\r
                    href="https://www.facebook.com/nextcodezz"\r
                    target="_blank"\r
                    className="underline"\r
                  >\r
                    Facebook\r
                  </a>\r
                </li>\r
              </ul>\r
            </div>\r
          </div>\r
          <div className="border-y-2 md:py-4 border-gray-200">\r
            <motion.svg\r
              width="776"\r
              ref={ref}\r
              height="137"\r
              viewBox="0 0 776 137"\r
              fill="none"\r
              className="sm:h-fit h-20 md:px-8 px-2 footer-logo w-full"\r
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"\r
              initial="hidden"\r
              animate={isInView ? 'visible' : 'hidden'}\r
            >\r
              {pathArr.map((path, index) => {\r
                return (\r
                  <>\r
                    <motion.path\r
                      custom={index}\r
                      variants={variants}\r
                      d={path}\r
                      fill="#3E7AEE"\r
                    />\r
                  </>\r
                )\r
              })}\r
            </motion.svg>\r
          </div>\r
          <div className="flex md:flex-row flex-col-reverse gap-3 justify-between py-2">\r
            <span className="font-medium">\r
              © 2023 NextCodez. All Rights Reserved.\r
            </span>\r
            <a href="#" className="font-semibold">\r
              Privacy Policy\r
            </a>\r
          </div>\r
        </div>\r
      </div>\r
    </>\r
  )\r
}\r
\r
export default Footer\r

import React, { useEffect, useRef, useState } from 'react'\r
import { cn } from '@/lib/utils'\r
\r
function index() {\r
  return (\r
    <>\r
      <footer\r
        className="footer-bg relative border 2xl:h-[550px] h-fit lg:pb-20 w-[95%] mx-auto mb-8 rounded-lg overflow-hidden radial-gradient-bg\r
                   [--gradient-center:#f3f4f6] [--gradient-edge:#f3f4f6]\r
                   dark:[--gradient-center:#02081765] dark:[--gradient-edge:#020817]"\r
      >\r
        <div className="gap-10 sm:flex justify-between p-5 2xl:py-10 py-5 dark:bg-[#4c61ff]   bg-blue-500 rounded-sm rounded-b-none text-white">\r
          <div className="w-fit flex-col  flex  justify-center">\r
            <div className="2xl:w-24 2xl:h-24 w-20 h-20 ml-3 bg-white  rounded-sm before:absolute relative before:w-full before:h-full before:bg-white/50  before:rounded-md before:-top-3 before:-left-3"></div>\r
            <article className="py-2  2xl:w-80 w-64  space-y-1">\r
              <h1 className="newFont text-3xl font-bold">UI-LAYOUT</h1>\r
              <p className="text-sm  leading-[120%] ">\r
                Copy and paste designs that you love to have on your website.\r
                Don't forget to share them with your friends. I'll bring more\r
                and more components that really make sense for your design.\r
              </p>\r
            </article>\r
          </div>\r
\r
          <div className="sm:block flex sm:mt-0 mt-4  gap-2 sm:w-auto w-full sm:space-y-2 relative z-[1]">\r
            <a\r
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/naymur-rahman/"\r
              target="_blank"\r
              className="bg-gray-50 sm:w-auto w-full   grid place-content-center 2xl:h-40 h-32 2xl:p-10 p-5 rounded-lg"\r
            >\r
              <svg\r
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"\r
                width="70"\r
                height="62"\r
                viewBox="0 0 70 62"\r
                fill="none"\r
                className="sm:w-24 w-full  text-blue-500"\r
              >\r
                <path\r
                  d="M55.1291 0H65.8629L42.4127 26.2626L70 62H48.3994L31.481 40.3254L12.1226 62H1.38228L26.4646 33.9092L0 0H22.149L37.4417 19.8114L55.1291 0ZM51.3619 55.7046H57.3096L18.9172 5.96472H12.5347L51.3619 55.7046Z"\r
                  fill="currentColor"\r
                ></path>\r
              </svg>\r
            </a>\r
            <a\r
              href="https://x.com/naymur_dev"\r
              target="_blank"\r
              className="bg-gray-50 sm:w-auto w-full  grid place-content-center  2xl:h-40 h-32 2xl:p-10 p-5 rounded-lg"\r
            >\r
              <svg\r
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"\r
                width="100%"\r
                height="100%"\r
                viewBox="0 0 80 78"\r
                fill="none"\r
                className="sm:w-24 w-full text-blue-500"\r
              >\r
                <path\r
                  d="M16.6 8.79036C16.6 13.3937 12.9 17.1237 8.33333 17.1237C3.76667 17.1237 0.0666667 13.3937 0.0666667 8.79036C0.0666667 4.19036 3.76667 0.457031 8.33333 0.457031C12.9 0.457031 16.6 4.19036 16.6 8.79036ZM16.6667 23.7904H0V77.1237H16.6667V23.7904ZM43.2733 23.7904H26.7133V77.1237H43.2767V49.127C43.2767 33.5604 63.3733 32.287 63.3733 49.127V77.1237H80V43.3537C80 17.087 50.26 18.0437 43.2733 30.9737V23.7904Z"\r
                  fill="currentColor"\r
                ></path>\r
              </svg>\r
            </a>\r
          </div>\r
        </div>\r
        <div className="lg:block hidden">\r
          <AnimatedText text="UI-LAYOUT" className="text-[10vw]" />\r
        </div>\r
      </footer>\r
    </>\r
  )\r
}\r
\r
interface AnimatedTextProps {\r
  text: string\r
  className?: string\r
}\r
\r
export const AnimatedText: React.FC<AnimatedTextProps> = ({\r
  text,\r
  className,\r
}) => {\r
  const [mousePosition, setMousePosition] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 })\r
  const textRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\r
\r
  useEffect(() => {\r
    const handleMouseMove = (event: MouseEvent) => {\r
      if (textRef.current) {\r
        const rect = textRef.current.getBoundingClientRect()\r
        setMousePosition({\r
          x: event.clientX - rect.left,\r
          y: event.clientY - rect.top,\r
        })\r
      }\r
    }\r
\r
    window.addEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove)\r
\r
    return () => {\r
      window.removeEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove)\r
    }\r
  }, [])\r
\r
  return (\r
    <div\r
      ref={textRef}\r
      className={cn(\r
        \`animated-text  text-[17vw] text-center tracking-[-0.06em] w-full font-bold left-0 -bottom-4 absolute leading-[80%]\r
                 [--gradient-text-center:#3a7eee] [--gradient-text-edge:#f3f4f6]\r
                 dark:[--gradient-text-center:rgb(226,226,226)] dark:[--gradient-text-edge:rgba(0,9,12,0.1)]\`,\r
        className\r
      )}\r
      style={\r
        {\r
          '--text-mouse-x': \`\${mousePosition.x}px\`,\r
          '--text-mouse-y': \`\${mousePosition.y}px\`,\r
        } as React.CSSProperties\r
      }\r
    >\r
      {text}\r
    </div>\r
  )\r
}\r
\r
export default index

AnimatedTextProps {\r
  text: string\r
  className?: string\r
}\r
\r
export const AnimatedText: React.FC<AnimatedTextProps> = ({\r
  text,\r
  className,\r
}) => {\r
  const [mousePosition, setMousePosition] = useState({ x: 0, y: 0 })\r
  const textRef = useRef<HTMLDivElement>(null)\r
\r
  useEffect(() => {\r
    const handleMouseMove = (event: MouseEvent) => {\r
      if (textRef.current) {\r
        const rect = textRef.current.getBoundingClientRect()\r
        setMousePosition({\r
          x: event.clientX - rect.left,\r
          y: event.clientY - rect.top,\r
        })\r
      }\r
    }\r
\r
    window.addEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove)\r
\r
    return () => {\r
      window.removeEventListener('mousemove', handleMouseMove)\r
    }\r
  }, [])\r
\r
  return (\r
    <div\r
      ref={textRef}\r
      className={cn(\r
        \`animated-text  text-center tracking-[-0.06em] w-full font-bold left-0 -bottom-4 absolute leading-[80%]\r
                 [--gradient-text-center:#3a7eee] [--gradient-text-edge:#f3f4f6]\r
                 dark:[--gradient-text-center:rgb(226,226,226)] dark:[--gradient-text-edge:rgba(0,9,12,0.1)]\`,\r
        className\r
      )}\r
      style={\r
        {\r
          '--text-mouse-x': \`\${mousePosition.x}px\`,\r
          '--text-mouse-y': \`\${mousePosition.y}px\`,\r
        } as React.CSSProperties\r
      }\r
    >\r
      {text}\r
    </div>\r
  )\r
}
